--       A_Generic_Function_Renaming
--       A_Generic_Package_Renaming
--       A_Procedure_Body
--       A_Function_Body
--       A_Package_Body
--
--  Returns Unit_Kinds:
--       Not_A_Unit
--       A_Package
--       A_Generic_Package
--       A_Package_Instance
--       A_Nonexistent_Declaration
--       An_Unknown_Unit
--
--  If a parent is inconsistent with a child passed as the argument,
